She was known for being Hustlers first contract model and the "Hustler Honey of the Year" in 2004 and the August 2008 Penthouse Pet of the Month. She was born in Anchorage, Alaska. Her career began in 2002. Jaymes played a small role in two episodes of the television series Weeds in 2006 and 2007,"Jessica Jaymes Official Site", entries of June 6, 2007 through September 3, 2007. Retrieved September 30, 2007. and made appearances on various reality shows such as VH1's Celebrity Rehab Sober House and HBO's Vivid Valley as well as The Howard Stern Show. Jaymes was found dead at her home in San Fernando Valley, California on September 17, 2019 at the age of 40.Porn star Jessica Jaymes dead at 40 The Los Angeles County Coroner said that her cause of death was from a seizure and alcohol abuse. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1979 births Category:2019 deaths Category:American pornographic actors Category:American television actors Category:American models Category:Actors from Anchorage, Alaska
